■In memory of
Evelyn R Wheeldon
1934 - 2016
Loving mother of seven boys and one girl
and aunt to Carol and Pam also here on this bench.
Remembered and loved by all who knew her

Frances Kathleen Hall (Shale)
Jan 9th 1924- Feb 24th 1995
Sister to Evelyn and three others, Mother to Carol, Pam
and 9 others, Grandmother to lots and Great Grandmother
Enjoy the view and company

Carol Ann Bond
17/12/1945 - 10/05/2014
The bestest 'Mommykins' ever
Much loved Mom (to 6 girls), Sister (to 10), Wife,
Nan, Great Grandmother and great friend.
Enjoy your view, you will be missed. Love you always.

In memory of our beautiful Mim and Nanny
Pamela June Wootton
05/01/1951- 17/01/2015
Reunited with her big sister Carol (Ginge)
Always loved and forever in our hearts
